summoning forth visitors from heaven.

1762
01:42:47,979 --> 01:42:50,812
We all became immediate
fans of Shia LaBeouf,

1763
01:42:50,899 --> 01:42:52,537
because our robots are worth nothing

1764
01:42:52,619 --> 01:42:54,257
