of emotion from a robot

1811
01:45:32,539 --> 01:45:34,097
if you don't have things that move.

1812
01:45:34,179 --> 01:45:35,897
Michael stressed to us
how important it was

1813
01:45:35,979 --> 01:45:38,891
to get the performance
to read in the eyes.

1814
01:45:38,979 --> 01:45:40,810
The majority of the performance
is sold in the eyes.

1815
01:45:40,899 --> 01:45:43,254
The more we added,
it just made it more real

1816
01:45:43,339 --> 01:45:45,250
and felt like
there's a soul in there.

1817
01:45:45,339 --> 01:45:47,728
My name is Optimus Prime.

1818
01:45:47,819 --> 01:45:51,732
We are autonomous robotic organisms
from the planet Cybertron.

1819
01:45:57,379 --> 01:45:59,097
We have a lot of
transforming robots.

